<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order confirmation</title>

    <style>
        body{
            font-family:"sans-serif";
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
max-width: 600px;
height: 100vh; margin: auto;
padding: 20px;
background-color:
#4f5ef1;
box-shadow: 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
color: #ffffff;
}
.message{
text-align: center;
font-size: 18px; 
margin-bottom: 20px; 
padding-top: 50px;
}
.course-name {
font-size: 24px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
} 
.purchase-info {
font-size: 16px;
} 
.total {
font-size: 18px; 
text-align: right; 
margin-top: 20px;
} 
.footer {
text-align: center; 
margin-top: 100px;
color: #fff;
}

.flex{
    display: flex;
    display: inline-block;
    color: #fff;
}
.footer>p> a { 
    text-decoration: none; 
    display: inline-block; 
    color: #fff;
}
.flex h4 {
font-weight: 400;
 margin-bottom: 5px;
}
.flex.lg {
width: 85%;
margin: auto;
border-bottom: none;
}
.first-td {
text-transform: uppercase;
 color: #000006;
  padding: 5px 0px;
font-size: 16px;
width: 1%;
}
.first-td {
font-weight: 600 !important;
} 
.second-td{
font-weight: 500 !important;
 color: #000ee0af; 
 font-size: 15px;}
.title{
    font-size: 16px !important
}
table {
 border-collapse: collapse;
width: 100%;
}
td {
padding: 10px; text-align: center; width: 28133%;
}
td.col-2 {
width: 100%;
text-align: left; padding: 0px;
margin: 0;}

.m-auto {
width: 100%; margin: auto; }
.table-row {
width: 70%; display: block; margin: auto; padding: 10px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<div class="message-sm">
<h1>Your ELearning order is confirmed!</h1>
 <p> And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
</div>
<br/>
<br/>
<div class="course-info">
<h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
<table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f;">
<tr>
<td>
Order #:<%= order._id %>
</td>
<td>
    <%= order.data %>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block">
<tr>
<td class="first-td">Item</td>
<td class="first-td">Qty</td>
</tr>
<td class="first-td">cost</td>
</table>
<table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block">
<tr class="second-td" >$<%order.name> </tr>
<td class="second-td">1</td>
<td class="second-td"> $<%order.price> </td>
</tr>
</table>

<table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #00000029;">
<tr>
<td class="col-2">Subtotal:</td>
<td class="col-2">$ order.price></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table class="table-row" style="margin-top: -20px;">
<tr>
<td class="col-2">Total:</td>
<td class="col-2">$ order.price</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
<div class="footer">
<p>
If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:dhanusmc93@gmail.com">dhanusmc93@gmail.com</a>
</p>
<p>&copy; 2023 Elearning. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>